{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"14540abc10","title":"短章组诗","origin":"原载一九五七年六月號《詩刊》，见江东语文网（jdyuwen.com.cn）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"aaf1525a74","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"14540abc10"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"ded099315a","name":"北京市汪曾祺"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2c90eb4437","type":"title","text":"短章组诗","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"14540abc10"},{"id":"0a9e5f6588","type":"authors","text":"北京市汪曾祺","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"14540abc10"},{"id":"ef9ac74dfe","type":"paragraph","text":"〈彩旗〉","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"14540abc10"},{"id":"44832b56d7","type":"paragraph","text":"当风的彩旗，像一片被缚住的波浪。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"14540abc10"},{"id":"96e9332daa","type":"paragraph","text":"〈杏花〉","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"14540abc10"},{"id":"826b29be6a","type":"paragraph","text":"杏花翻着碎碎的瓣子……仿佛有人拿了一桶花瓣散在树上。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"14540abc10"},{"id":"b9f09384b4","type":"paragraph","text":"〈早春〉","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"14540abc10"},{"id":"1cd982b1c7","type":"paragraph","text":"新绿是朦胧的，飘浮在树杪，完全不像是叶子……远树的绿色的呼吸。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"14540abc10"},{"id":"43a0dd50e7","type":"paragraph","text":"〈黄昏〉","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"14540abc10"},{"id":"5a1b18cdd9","type":"paragraph","text":"青灰色的黄昏，","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"14540abc10"},{"id":"429c956595","type":"paragraph","text":"下班的时候。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"14540abc10"},{"id":"ac132573aa","type":"paragraph","text":"暗绿的道旁的柏树，银红的骑车女郎的帽子，橘黄色的电车灯。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"14540abc10"},{"id":"20cf91a10e","type":"paragraph","text":"忽然路灯亮了，","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"14540abc10"},{"id":"e737c5fa25","type":"paragraph","text":"（像是轻轻地拍了拍手……）","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"14540abc10"},{"id":"b5440d393e","type":"paragraph","text":"空气里扩散着早春的湿润。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"14540abc10"},{"id":"6cfe7bb1d3","type":"paragraph","text":"〈火车〉","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"14540abc10"},{"id":"74f03ed3d6","type":"paragraph","text":"火车开过来了。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"14540abc10"},{"id":"b3d27b3066","type":"paragraph","text":"鲜洁，明亮，刷洗得清清爽爽，好像闻得到车厢里甘凉的空气。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"14540abc10"},{"id":"a032939417","type":"paragraph","text":"这是餐车，窗纱整齐地挽着，每个窗口放着一盆鲜花。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"14540abc10"},{"id":"fd368f6caa","type":"paragraph","text":"火车是空的。火车正在调进车站，去接纳去往各地的旅客。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"14540abc10"},{"id":"59529ec51c","type":"paragraph","text":"火车开过去了，突突突突，突突突突……火车喷出来的气是灰蓝色的，蓝得那样深，简直走不过一个人去；但是，很快，在它经过你的面前的时候，它映出早已是 眼睛看不出来的夕阳的余光，变成极其柔和的浅红色；终于撕成一片白色的碎片，像正常的蒸汽的颜色，翻卷着，疾速地消灭在高空。于是，天色暗下来了。?","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"14540abc10"}],"page":{"id":"d1c955f4f3","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"14540abc10","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}